<%- include('../partials/header') %>
<%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

<div class="container">
    <div class="form-container" style="max-width: 800px; padding: 3rem;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 2.4rem; color: var(--primary-dark); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: left;">About ACT Market</h2>
        
        <p style="text-align: left; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-main); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            Welcome to the <strong>ACT Student Marketplace</strong>! This platform is designed specifically for students at the <strong>American College of Technology (ACT)</strong> to buy, sell, and trade textbook copies, laptops, phones, desk lamps, backpacks, and other campus essentials.
        </p>

        <p style="text-align: left; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-main); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            Whether you are joining as a freshman looking to acquire cheap study books or a graduating senior looking to offload old room furniture, ACT Market makes student-to-student transactions straightforward and safe.
        </p>

        <h3 style="font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--primary); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Our Mission</h3>
        <p style="text-align: left; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            To support student sustainability, reduce academic material expenses, and foster a connected community by providing an easy-to-use digital trading post exclusively within the ACT campus circle.
        </p>

        <h3 style="font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--primary); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">How it works</h3>
        <ul style="text-align: left; font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text-muted); padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; line-height: 1.8;">
            <li><strong>Register:</strong> Sign up with your university credentials and Student ID.</li>
            <li><strong>List items:</strong> Take photos of items you no longer need, describe them, set a price, and publish.</li>
            <li><strong>Trade:</strong> Buyers contact sellers directly via email or the messaging system to arrange convenient hand-overs on campus.</li>
        </ul>

        <div style="text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color); padding-top: 2rem;">
            <a href="/listings" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-right: 1rem;">Start Browsing</a>
            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-secondary">Create Account</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
